Package: fabR
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper Functions Collection Used In Data Pipelines 
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Guillaume Fabre
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Guillaume",
             family = "Fabre",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "guijoseph.fabre@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Guillaume Fabre <guijoseph.fabre@gmail.com> 
Description: The goal of this package is to provide wrapper functions in the data 
    cleaning and cleansing processe. These function helps in messages and interaction
    with the user, keep track of information in pipelines, help in the wrangling,
    munging, assessement and visualization of data frame-like material.
License: GPL-3
